{"tid":1175852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★綜援婦清水填肚 寧餵飽兩女","createTime":"2019-05-28T23:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T12:08:08.000Z","uid":21598,"like":10,"dislike":486,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"8b96306ada83fc3513493da46566e7dffea2d037","tid":1175852,"uid":21598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20080723/large/23la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080723%2Flarge%2F23la2p2.jpg&h=37034e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n領取綜援的阿英寧可自己捱餓，喝清水來填肚，也要讓兩個女兒吃得飽，因此經常感到頭暈。 <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「我有時早、午兩餐夾埋食六蚊腸粉就算，有時會餓到頭暈，不過肚餓咪飲水頂住個肚！寧願慳埋畀兩個女食飽。」於02年來港的38歲新移民阿英，與兩個女兒拿取每月4,000幾元綜援；食物價格不斷上升，綜援加幅追不上通脹，苦上加苦。關注綜援檢討聯盟指現時的綜援制度太落後，政府的紓困措施只能短暫幫助綜援家庭。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6wOvQBg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wOvQBg.gif&h=1371c900&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3354e7ad5527dd8e7da0526f3159e7202ac1310e","tid":1175852,"uid":120070,"like":381,"dislike":3,"score":378,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:54:47.000Z","msg":"好慘呀 盡力 講到最慘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（ 屌你老母 唔躝翻大陸？） <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50211e389bfbb05955d2debe8b41308702d0612b","tid":1175852,"uid":11540,"like":856,"dislike":4,"score":852,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:55:55.000Z","msg":"屌你飲水飲到咁撚大隻可唔可以教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd15c44ea4e10a27be2faae37997b4337cfa60e","tid":1175852,"uid":132478,"like":163,"dislike":2,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T23:56:00.000Z","msg":"大陸啲野平啲<img src